query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(cn mc) NoMergeJoin(cn mc t) NoMergeJoin(cn mc t ci) NoHashJoin(ci cn mc t a1) NoMergeJoin(a1 ci cn mc t n1) NoMergeJoin(a1 ci cn mc n1 t rt) */ select min(a1.name) AS writer_pseudo_name,
min(t.title) AS movie_title
from company_name AS cn
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code = '[ru]'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = t.id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
inner join aka_name AS a1
on a1.person_id = ci.person_id
inner join name AS n1
on a1.person_id = n1.id AND n1.id = ci.person_id
inner join role_type AS rt
on ci.role_id = rt.id AND rt.role = 'writer';
